{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "plumbmanager-vendor-api-v1",
		"name": "PlumbManager — Vendor App API",
		"description": "# PlumbManager Vendor App API\n\nPartner/vendor mobile app API (`/api/v2/*`).\n\n---\n\n## Quick Start\n\n| Step | Action |\n|------|--------|\n| 1 | Import this collection + **PlumbManager Vendor App — Local** environment |\n| 2 | Set `base_url` (default `http://127.0.0.1:8001`) |\n| 3 | Run **01 Auth → Send OTP (Vendor Login)** then **Verify OTP (Vendor Login)** |\n| 4 | Token auto-saves to `{{token}}` |\n\n---\n\n## Auth Flows\n\n### Login (existing vendor)\n1. `POST /auth/send-otp` — `{ mobile, type: \"vendor_login\" }` → returns `otp`\n2. `POST /auth/verify-otp` — `{ mobile, otp, type: \"vendor_login\" }` → returns `token` + `user`\n\nAlternative: `POST /auth/login` — `{ mobile, otp }`\n\n### Register (new vendor)\n1. `POST /auth/send-otp` — `{ mobile, type: \"vendor_register\" }`\n2. `POST /auth/verify-otp` — `{ mobile, otp, type: \"vendor_register\" }` → `{ verified: true }`\n3. `POST /auth/register` — multipart with owner + shop + bank details\n\n---\n\n## OTP Types\n\n| App | Login | Register |\n|-----|-------|----------|\n| Vendor | `vendor_login` | `vendor_register` |\n\n---\n\n## Response Format\n\n```json\n{ \"success\": true, \"message\": \"...\", \"data\": { ... } }\n```\n\n---\n\n## Auth Header (Protected Routes)\n\n```\nAuthorization: Bearer {{token}}\nAccept: application/json\n```",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{ "key": "base_url", "value": "http://127.0.0.1:8001" },
		{ "key": "token", "value": "" },
		{ "key": "mobile", "value": "9512345872" },
		{ "key": "register_mobile", "value": "9512345999" },
		{ "key": "otp", "value": "" },
		{ "key": "order_id", "value": "1" },
		{ "key": "product_id", "value": "1" },
		{ "key": "category_id", "value": "1" },
		{ "key": "subcategory_id", "value": "1" },
		{ "key": "fcm_token", "value": "" },
		{ "key": "notification_id", "value": "1" }
	],
	"auth": {
		"type": "bearer",
		"bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
	},
	"event": [
		{
			"listen": "prerequest",
			"script": {
				"type": "text/javascript",
				"exec": ["pm.request.headers.upsert({ key: 'Accept', value: 'application/json' });"]
			}
		}
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "00 — App Screen Flows",
			"description": "End-to-end flows matching the Partner Dashboard mobile app screens.",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Flow A — Vendor Login",
					"item": [
						{
							"name": "A1 Send OTP (Vendor Login)",
							"event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": [
								"const j = pm.response.json();",
								"if (j.data?.otp) { pm.collectionVariables.set('otp', String(j.data.otp)); pm.environment.set('otp', String(j.data.otp)); console.log('OTP: ' + j.data.otp); }",
								"pm.test('OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
							]}}],
							"request": { "auth": { "type": "noauth" }, "method": "POST", "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
								"body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"mobile\": \"{{mobile}}\",\n  \"type\": \"vendor_login\"\n}" },
								"url": "{{base_url}}/api/v2/auth/send-otp",
								"description": "**Screen:** Login → Enter mobile → Get OTP" }
						},
						{
							"name": "A2 Verify OTP (Vendor Login)",
							"event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": [
								"const j = pm.response.json();",
								"if (j.data?.token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('token', j.data.token); pm.environment.set('token', j.data.token); }",
								"pm.test('OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
							]}}],
							"request": { "auth": { "type": "noauth" }, "method": "POST", "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
								"body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"mobile\": \"{{mobile}}\",\n  \"otp\": {{otp}},\n  \"type\": \"vendor_login\",\n  \"fcm_token\": \"{{fcm_token}}\"\n}" },
								"url": "{{base_url}}/api/v2/auth/verify-otp",
								"description": "**Screen:** Enter OTP → Login (returns token)" }
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"name": "Flow B — Vendor Register (3 screens)",
					"item": [
						{
							"name": "B1 Send OTP (Vendor Register)",
							"event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": [
								"const j = pm.response.json();",
								"if (j.data?.otp) { pm.collectionVariables.set('otp', String(j.data.otp)); pm.environment.set('otp', String(j.data.otp)); console.log('OTP: ' + j.data.otp); }",
								"pm.test('OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
							]}}],
							"request": { "auth": { "type": "noauth" }, "method": "POST", "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
								"body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"mobile\": \"{{register_mobile}}\",\n  \"type\": \"vendor_register\"\n}" },
								"url": "{{base_url}}/api/v2/auth/send-otp",
								"description": "Use a mobile number that is not already registered." }
						},
						{
							"name": "B2 Verify OTP (Vendor Register)",
							"event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": [
								"const j = pm.response.json();",
								"pm.test('Verified', () => pm.expect(j.data?.verified).to.eql(true));",
								"pm.test('OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
							]}}],
							"request": { "auth": { "type": "noauth" }, "method": "POST", "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
								"body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"mobile\": \"{{register_mobile}}\",\n  \"otp\": {{otp}},\n  \"type\": \"vendor_register\"\n}" },
								"url": "{{base_url}}/api/v2/auth/verify-otp",
								"description": "Verifies OTP only. Complete signup in next step." }
						},
						{
							"name": "B3 Register (Owner + Shop + Bank)",
							"event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": [
								"const j = pm.response.json();",
								"if (j.data?.token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('token', j.data.token); pm.environment.set('token', j.data.token); }",
								"pm.test('OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));"
							]}}],
							"request": { "auth": { "type": "noauth" }, "method": "POST",
								"body": { "mode": "formdata", "formdata": [
									{ "key": "name", "value": "Sarah", "type": "text", "description": "Owner Details — Full Name" },
									{ "key": "mobile", "value": "{{register_mobile}}", "type": "text" },
									{ "key": "email", "value": "sarah@gmail.com", "type": "text" },
									{ "key": "aadhar_card", "type": "file", "src": [], "description": "Owner Details — Aadhar Card" },
									{ "key": "shop_name", "value": "Sarah Plumbing Mart", "type": "text", "description": "Shop Details" },
									{ "key": "business_mobile", "value": "{{register_mobile}}", "type": "text" },
									{ "key": "shop_email", "value": "shop.sarah@gmail.com", "type": "text" },
									{ "key": "gst_number", "value": "27AABCS1234A1Z5", "type": "text" },
									{ "key": "address", "value": "123, ABC Road, XYZ Area", "type": "text" },
									{ "key": "country", "value": "India", "type": "text" },
									{ "key": "state", "value": "M.P", "type": "text" },
									{ "key": "city", "value": "Indore", "type": "text" },
									{ "key": "pincode", "value": "452001", "type": "text" },
									{ "key": "shop_logo", "type": "file", "src": [], "description": "Shop Details — Logo" },
									{ "key": "pan_card", "type": "file", "src": [], "description": "Shop Details — PAN Card" },
									{ "key": "account_holder_name", "value": "Sarah", "type": "text", "description": "Bank Details" },
									{ "key": "account_number", "value": "951234587254", "type": "text" },
									{ "key": "ifsc_code", "value": "HDFC0001234", "type": "text" },
									{ "key": "bank_name", "value": "Bank Of Mirzapur", "type": "text" },
									{ "key": "account_type", "value": "savings", "type": "text", "description": "savings or current" }
								] },
								"url": "{{base_url}}/api/v2/auth/register",
								"description": "Multipart register — Owner Details + Shop Details + Bank Details. Status starts as pending." }
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"name": "Flow C — Partner Dashboard (Home)",
					"item": [
